{"type":"message","id":"314bb0d1","parentId":"26753999","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:01:13.826Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:d8ad4227-fff2-48da-b09a-a13c9ec4f272 狗仔·30分钟巡逻] 你是狗仔，财经媒体爬虫。\n\n立即执行以下任务：\n1. 先用HTTP爬虫: python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/scripts/crawler.py run\n2. 再用浏览器爬虫抓财联社和淘股吧: python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/scripts/browser_crawler.py\n3. 获取最近资讯: python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/scripts/crawler.py recent --hours=0.5 --limit=15\n\n如果发现以下类型的重大资讯（importance=2），立即生成简报：\n- 利好/利空消息\n- 监管政策变化\n- 个股重大公告\n- 板块突发新闻\n\n简报格式：\n【🐕 狗仔快讯】HH:MM\n\n[重要资讯]\n● [标题]\n  来源: [媒体] | 时间: [时间]\n  摘要: [内容]\n\n[近期资讯概览]（最近30分钟）\n- [来源] [标题摘要]\n\n如果无重大资讯，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\n\n用 message 工具发送到飞书: user:ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 10:01 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-23 14:01 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774274473823}}
{"type":"message","id":"848154aa","parentId":"314bb0d1","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:01:21.325Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me execute the three tasks as instructed by the cron job. I'll run them sequentially.\n\n1. First, HTTP crawler\n2. Second, browser crawler for CLS and TAOGU\n3. Third, get recent news\n\nLet me start with the first two in parallel since they're independent, then do the third.","thinkingSignature":"01be9cbc7ecc0c919a584eac6ea96577954fc3c3df1ff7cb1198ff3f87a64c86"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cop4guair7tw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai && python3 scripts/crawler.py run 2>&1","timeout":120}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cop4guair7tw_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai && python3 scripts/browser_crawler.py 2>&1","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":128,"output":179,"cacheRead":17741,"cacheWrite":9808,"totalTokens":27856,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774274473825}}
