{"type":"message","id":"13d3e638","parentId":"a4f3f6c1","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:01:45.302Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_r61m7mdh31l9_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[22:01:21] 狗仔开始巡逻...\n  财联社失败: 405 Client Error: Method Not Allowed for url: https://www.cls.cn/api/sw?app=CLS&os=web&sv=7.8.3&width=750&row=20&start=0&type=1,2,3&app_type=day\n  财联社: 抓取0条, 新增0条\n  东方财富: 抓取20条, 新增20条\n  同花顺: 抓取20条, 新增20条\n  雪球失败: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0)\n  雪球: 抓取0条, 新增0条\n  淘股吧失败: 400 Client Error: Bad Request for url: https://www.tgb.cn/api/article/list?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20&blockId=0&order=1\n  淘股吧: 抓取0条, 新增0条\n狗仔巡逻完毕: 共40条新资讯\n40\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"crisp-breeze","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[22:01:21] 狗仔开始巡逻...\n  财联社失败: 405 Client Error: Method Not Allowed for url: https://www.cls.cn/api/sw?app=CLS&os=web&sv=7.8.3&width=750&row=20&start=0&type=1,2,3&app_type=day\n  财联社: 抓取0条, 新增0条\n  东方财富: 抓取20条, 新增20条\n  同花顺: 抓取20条, 新增20条\n  雪球失败: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0)\n  雪球: 抓取0条, 新增0条\n  淘股吧失败: 400 Client Error: Bad Request for url: https://www.tgb.cn/api/article/list?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20&blockId=0&order=1\n  淘股吧: 抓取0条, 新增0条\n狗仔巡逻完毕: 共40条新资讯\n40\n","name":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774274505288}}
